                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-11-20T12:32:46.389-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="Unlocking knowledge with data"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text_copy_copy
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                    jcr:created="{Date}2022-12-07T14:53:09.069-05:00"
                                    jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-12-05T14:04:04.215-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>To speed up the pace of discovery, we developed the &lt;a href=&quot;/content/abbvie-com2/us/en/who-we-are/our-stories/meet-the-arch-a-time-saving-tool-for-researchers-focused-on-finding-cures.html&quot;>AbbVie R&amp;amp;D Convergence Hub (ARCH)&lt;/a>, an industry-leading analytics platform that helps us connect the dots of data like never before.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>In what is now one of the largest data-driven initiatives in the biopharma industry, ARCH uses cutting-edge AI and ML technologies to centralize and connect data from more than 200 internal and external sources, enabling our scientists to access and collaborate on over 2 billion points of knowledge.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Bringing together different types of data helps us to unlock new knowledge faster,  accelerate discovery of new drug targets, and optimize drug design, with the goal to bring new, more effective treatments to patients faster and more efficiently.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                                <separator
